file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  "/item":
    put:
      operationId: putItem
      summary: Put item
      responses:
        default:
          description: Error
    options:
      operationId: optionsItem
      summary: Options item
      responses:
        default:
          description: Error
components:
  schemas:
    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
      required:
        - code
        - message
